<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Prices - Furry Tails Photography</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <a href="/">Furry Tails Photography</a>
      </div>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/how-it-works">How It Works</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About Me</a></li>
        <li><a href="/prices">Prices</a></li>
        <li><a href="/gallery">Gallery</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Pricing</h1>
        <p>Affordable pet photography packages for every budget</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="pricing-grid">
          <div class="pricing-card">
            <h3>Basic Package</h3>
            <div class="price">$150</div>
            <ul class="features">
              <li>30-minute session</li>
              <li>Location of your choice</li>
              <li>20-30 edited digital photos</li>
              <li>Digital files via email</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Book Now</a>
          </div>

          <div class="pricing-card featured">
            <h3>Premium Package</h3>
            <div class="price">$300</div>
            <ul class="features">
              <li>60-minute session</li>
              <li>Multiple locations</li>
              <li>50-75 edited digital photos</li>
              <li>Digital files via secure cloud link</li>
              <li>One free reshoot if needed</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Book Now</a>
          </div>

          <div class="pricing-card">
            <h3>Group/Family Package</h3>
            <div class="price">$400</div>
            <ul class="features">
              <li>90-minute session</li>
              <li>Up to 3 pets (or pet + owner)</li>
              <li>75-100 edited digital photos</li>
              <li>Printed 8x10 photo</li>
              <li>Digital files via secure cloud link</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Book Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-notes">
          <h3>Add-ons</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Printed Prints:</strong> 8x10 ($25), 11x14 ($40), Canvas 12x16 ($80)</li>
            <li><strong>Album/Photobook:</strong> Starting at $50</li>
            <li><strong>Rush Editing:</strong> One-week turnaround (+$50)</li>
          </ul>

          <p>All packages include professional editing and high-resolution digital files. Don't see what you're looking for? <a href="/contact">Contact me</a> to discuss custom packages.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Furry Tails Photography. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p><a href="/contact">Get in touch</a></p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
